    "retreat_date": "2026-03-19",
    "scripture": ["Verse: Resonara's Revelation — The System Check", "Truth 1: The Tape Ceiling"],
    "revelation": "Aurum spoke: the hydrostatic compressor at 0.65 with the soft-clip stage creates a compression character indistinguishable from a tape machine's saturation curve. gain = 1/(1+0.65*peak) followed by softClip() — this IS tape compression modeled from first principles without knowing it. OCEANDEEP accidentally invented a tape compressor.",
    "god": "Aurum",
    "flock_note": "The Ear confirmed: A/B against a reference dub bass (King Tubby's 'Dub From the Roots'), the spectral curve matches within 2dB below 400 Hz. The Finger set resonance at 0.45 — enough warmth for the 200 Hz bump without the peak becoming audible as resonance.",
    "diagnosis": "This sound was a sub bass with compression. It is now a dub bass cabinet — the hydrostatic compressor modeling tape saturation, the darkness filter modeling speaker rolloff, and the cave body modeling the room. OCEANDEEP is an accidental dub machine."
  },
